oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Boy seated on bridge
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A country scene in Bradley County, Tennessee, showing a bridge over a creek with a cattle barrier beneath it. A boy, in overalls, sits on the bridge rails with his hands crossed in lap.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Wooden bridges; Bridge railings; Rural Children; Cattle guards
